briefTitle: BOTOX® Treatment for Adults With a Wide Lower Face Due to Masseter Muscle Prominence
officialTitle: BOTOX® (onabotulinumtoxinA) Treatment of Masseter Muscle Prominence: A Phase 3, Multicenter, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study
summary: This study is designed to evaluate the safety and effectiveness of administering BOTOX for the treatment of Masseter Muscle Prominence (MMP) in adults.

primaryOutcome.measure: Achievement of ≥ 2-Grade Improvement From Baseline on the Masseter Muscle Prominence Scale (MMPS) at Day 90
